snippet.title: Watamelon's Adventure V1.3 (Released) - NEW Trailer
snippet.description:
You are Watamelon, roll around, jump and collect Watamelon cards. Based on the meme of Tsunomaki Watame(lon), a vtuber.


Link to game: https://haslus.itch.io/watamelons-adventure
Link to Tsunomaki Watame's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqm3BQLlJfvkTsX_hvm0UmA
Source to the song of the video: https://youtu.be/6aaHNvAca1k
